task.summary: Moved animationtimer and scene to their own classes.
Implemented proper ShotPool for pooling shot entities.
Fixed that viewport would be reset to starting position once the animation is stopped.
Formatting and changed what kind of enemies are spawned.
Changed how game over is shown, fixed enemy shooting, more refactoring.
Removed output folder, because how did it get on git in the first place?
Moved most of the action to commands and implemented game saving/reloading using CTRL+S/CTRL+R
Moved most of logic to GameLogic class, fixed enemy direction saving and general refactoring.
Restructured for Maven and added 3 tests.
